node.text:
I challenge you TODAY to pick up the phone, call a friend, and share an idea with them. 🙌

When we collaboratively brainstorm our ideas, our concerns, our dreams with the people we trust and value most in our lives, we in return strengthen that bond. We become more authentically ourselves and promote creation, positivity, and change in the world!

Tag a friend in the comments below and share this clip with those in your life you generate ideas with 👏 👇

node.text:
Are you looking to elevate your leadership skills at work or at home? 🤔

One of the biggest roadblocks I see my coaching clients hit is that their team, their family, their community — they don't have any autonomy in the vision.

As a leader, it's your duty to include others in both the creating and deciding. When people can participate and have a hand in the creating process, they will be more engaged, excited, hardworking, and excellent! Remember — people support what they create!

So how are you performing as a leader? Are you allowing others to have a real contribution and a voice in the process? This is SUCH an important question to ask yourself and reflect on when you're in a leadership role. 👏

Comment below with some leadership techniques you are striving to be better at! 👇

#leadership #team #communication #voice #ideas #participation #leader #influence #personaldevelopment #teaching #wisdom #motivation #thebrendonshow #decisionsdecisions #decision

node.text:
People want a voice in the decision-making! 📣 

As a leader, it is your duty to honor that, celebrate that, and intentionally practice that by allowing your team members to participate in those needle-moving conversations. When people feel like they have skin in the game, when they feel like they are actively contributing and a part of the creation, they will support you and your mission. 

You set the standard for what kind of team and communication will transpire. So be that positive example and influence for your team! Allow them a space to feel seen, heard, and appreciated for their ideas. 

That, my friends, is the defining duty and quality that separates a good leader from a GREAT one. 👏

#leadership #team #communication #voice #ideas #participation #leader #influence #personaldevelopment #teaching #wisdom #motivation #thebrendonshow #decision

node.text:
You might be getting a lot done, BUT…if you don’t feel aligned, you’re getting the WRONG things done. 

Listen — things are going to feel hard to you if they are not:

▶️ in alignment with your true passions and interests
▶️ bringing up curiosity and enthusiasm
▶️ filling you up when you’re doing it

So if you’re wondering why you just can’t get into something or you’ve lost your motivation, it’s not that something is wrong with you. Maybe something simply isn’t in alignment for you.

Think about it. Does that feel true?

Some #tuesdaythoughts for you, and cheering you on along the way. Your coach,
- Brendon.

#leadership #leadingothers #motivation #selfawareness #selfimprovement #selfgrowth #growthday #alignment #beinginalignment #passion #curiosity #enthusiasm

node.text:
As a leader, do you give your team true AUTONOMY over their work and priorities? 🤔

It's time you trust in your team and lean in for support. You hired them because you saw their talent, potential for growth, and heart. Let them soar and lead with authenticity. Let them serve the mission proud! 

When you develop that trust — that is when the magic starts to happen, my friends. 💥

#thebrendonshow #trust #team #autonomy #leadership #motivation #wisdom

node.text:
"Brendon, you're CRAZY!" Just hear me out, okay? I know SO many couples who have all the love in the world, but without enthusiasm, without vibrancy, without spark, there will always be something missing. 🤭

It's time you really dig deep and take a closer look at your relationship. Are you and your partner *excited* about sharing and building a life together? Do you tackle your problems with real *enthusiasm* for the solution? 

I'm telling y'all, this is the secret ingredient to any successful relationship. I challenge you to lean into this idea. Show up for your partner. Bring aliveness and excitement to your relationship — for better or for worse. When you treat your joy and your conflict with the same enthusiasm, when you share a passion to build your futures together, when you face your problems head-on, THAT is when the magic starts. ❤️

#relationships #love #enthusiasm #vibrancy #relationshipadvice #marriage #partner #teamwork #conflict #growthday #lifecoach #aliveness #fridaymotivation

node.text:
The strongest relationships are built on encouragement. 🙌

The ability to encourage one another is SO vital. In research on relationships, we’ve found that happy couples tend to praise each other FIVE TIMES more than they complain or negate. 🤯

So with your partner, how often are you...
👉 Praising them?
👉 Encouraging them?
👉 Cheering them on?

What are the ways you can build more enthusiasm into your relationship? I know it sounds so simple, but watch how things change once you decide to prioritize this.

#wisdomwednesday #relationshipadvice #relationships #healthyrelationships #communication #healthycommunication #buildingtrust #enthusiasm #personalgrowth

node.text:
I challenge you TODAY to pick up the phone, call a friend, and share an idea with them. 🙌

When we collaboratively brainstorm our ideas, our concerns, our dreams with the people we trust and value most in our lives, we in return strengthen that bond. We become more authentically ourselves and promote creation, positivity, and change in the world!

Tag a friend in the comments below and share this clip with those in your life you generate ideas with 👏 👇

#friendships #relationships #makeadifference #positivty #thebrendonshow #ideas #share #creation #bond #authetic #changetheworld #motivation #personaldevelopment #generateideas #pickupthephone #wisdom

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Brendon Burchard on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'See yourself as a person who loves challenge and go for the big dreams. You are stronger than you think, and the future holds good things for you. Sure, you might fail. Sure, it might be uncomfortable. But what's the alternative? Holding back? Landing at the tail end of life and feeling that you didn't give it your all? Trudging through life safely inside your little bubble bored or complacent? Don't let that be your fate. @brendonburchard'.

Summon the best of you in some way, every day. The rest takes care of itself. 

#consistency #choice #selfreliance #motivation #growthmindset #personaldevelopment @growthday

node.text:
Are you looking to elevate your leadership skills at work or at home? 🤔

One of the biggest roadblocks I see my coaching clients hit is that their team, their family, their community — they don't have any autonomy in the vision.

As a leader, it's your duty to include others in both the creating and deciding. When people can participate and have a hand in the creating process, they will be more engaged, excited, hardworking, and excellent! Remember — people support what they create!

So how are you performing as a leader? Are you allowing others to have a real contribution and a voice in the process? This is SUCH an important question to ask yourself and reflect on when you're in a leadership role. 👏

Comment below with some leadership techniques you are striving to be better at! 👇

#leadership #team #communication #voice #ideas #participation #leader #influence #personaldevelopment #teaching #wisdom #motivation #thebrendonshow #decisionsdecisions #decision

node.text:
Who’s doing this? Gimme a YES if this is you! 👇

Most of the time, life will be filled with more “mundane” moments than BIG, life-changing moments. It’s your job to bring joy, meaning, and fulfillment to your day. Doesn’t mean you won’t face hardship, that you won’t agree with many things, or that some things are just tough and that’s that. But the more you can call in and SUMMON your enthusiasm for the day, the more life feels incredible.

#imagination #bringthejoy #intention #motivation #selfgrowth #inspiration #lifequotes #motivationalquotes #personaldevelopment #selfimprovement #growthday #letsgo #discipline #focus #reels #meaning #fulfillment #joy #presence #enthusiasm #wintheday
